data.description: Prestigious Woods & Meadows Chaffey home offers 4,178 sq ft of well-appointed living space. Stately covered entry, lofty ceilings, magnificent staircase. Formal living & dining rooms & family room. Enormous main level rec room! Kitchen w/red oak cabinets, stainless appliances, sunny breakfast nook. Primary suite w/walk in closet, & private bath w/soaking tub. 3 guest beds share 2 full baths. Den/office, huge bonus room, 2nd staircase. Energy efficient heat pump keeps utilities low. 3 car garage, level half acre lot w/adjacent greenbelt for permanent vegetation buffer. Minutes to schools, shopping, restaurants, trails & beaches. A truly impressive package!
